Package: conditionalSample
Type: Package
Title: Allows samples to be drawn from (generalized) linear models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-07-25
Author: Mark Hagemann
Maintainer: <mark.hagemann@gmail.com>
Description: Currently contains two functions, the most important of which is condlSample. 
  Useful either for generating pseudo-random data from a model, or alternatively for 
  getting conditional quantiles from a model. 
License: GNU GPL something something...
